    Address
    This class encapsulates address information
    Composer
    This class extends Person to create Composer.
    Composition
    This class encapsulates information related to pieces of music, specifically a composition of one or more movements.
    CompositionBuilder
    CompositionBuilder is used to build Composition.
    Concert
    This class uses ConcertBuilder to create a Concert.
    ConcertBuilder
    ConcertBuilder is used to build Concert.
    Conductor
    This class extends Person to create Conductor.
    Controller
    Controller builds objects from data in the symphony management database and builds them to add to a concert and add concerts to the Season.
    Credit
    Represents a debit transaction Has an identifer, a date and a debit cart associated with the transaction
    CreditCard
    The CreditCard class stores information related to a physical credit card.
    Customer
    This class extends Person to create Customer.
    Date
    This class builds a full date by utilizing a DateBuilder class
    DateBuilder
    This class helps to assemble all date components together and is used by Date class
    Day
    This class builds a Day parameter
    Debit
    Represents a debit transaction Has an identifer, a date and a debit cart associated with the transaction
    DebitCard
    The DebitCard class represents the information related to a physical debit card.
    Identification
    This class verifies the identification (ID) of the person.
    Month
    This class encapsulates a value representing a month in a date stamp.
    Movement
    This class uses MovementBuilder to create a Movement.
    MovementBuilder
    MovementBuilder is used to build Movement.
    Name
    This class encapsulates a string that represents a persons name.
    Performance<Composition>
    Performance extends ArrayList with Composition as the generic.
    Person
    This abstract class represents a person with name, address, phone number.
    Phone
    This class encapsulates a string that represents a telephone number.
    Season
    The season class represents a season that has scheduled a number of concerts.
    Soloist
    This class extends Person to create Soloist.
    Ticket
    Ticket creates a ticket that belongs to a Venue and is used by Transaction.
    Time
    The time class encapsulated data used to represent a time stamp
    Transaction  
    Venue
    Venue creates a venue to be used by Concert and Ticket.
    Year
    The year class encapsulates an integer that represents a year.
